{"word":"πυρόω","slug":"πυρόω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>πυρόω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:πῦρ\">πῦρ</a></el>] ‘cause to burn’, in <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ NT\">NT</a> only <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pass.\">pass.</a> <b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp> be set ablaze <a href='B:680 3:12'>2 Pt 3:12</a>;</b> in dramatic imagery <b><a href='B:560 6:16'>Eph 6:16</a>.</b> In <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ ext.\">ext.</a> sense, of strong emotion <b>burn <a href='B:530 7:9'>1 Cor 7:9</a>; <a href='B:540 11:29'>2 Cor 11:29</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> focus on intensity of heat <b>be made glowing hot,</b> of refining process <b><a href='B:730 1:15'>Rv 1:15</a>; <a href='B:730 3:18'>3:18</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:πύρινος\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:πυρράζω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}